Installation
1. Clone the Repository
Clone this repository to your local machine:

bash
Copy code
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/TastyBites-Recipe-Hub.git
2. Replace the API Key
Open the script.js file in a code editor.
Replace YOUR_API_KEY with your actual Spoonacular API key.
3. Open the Application
Once the API key is set, open index.html in your preferred browser to start using the app.

bash
Copy code
open index.html
Usage
--> Upon opening the app, you will see a search bar where you can enter the name of a recipe (e.g., "pizza", "pasta").
--> As you type, the app will make API requests to Spoonacular and fetch matching recipes.
--> The recipes will be displayed as cards, each containing an image, title, and a link to the full recipe.
--> Clicking on the "View Recipe" link will open the full recipe page on Spoonacular.
